                            <comment id="53458" author="jay" created="Wed, 6 Mar 2013 13:29:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;patch is at: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/5617&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/5617&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53446" author="jay" created="Wed, 6 Mar 2013 10:52:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Apparently when it tried to swap layout, the dd process wasn&apos;t even started to copy file. Usually the script sleeps a little while to yield CPU but it&apos;s broken sometimes on a busy VM.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think we need a reliable way to yield CPU and make sure the execution order of processes. It will be implemented in framework.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
